01:22:23.130 --> 01:22:24.429
Pronto, Charles?

1214
01:22:25.039 --> 01:22:26.237
Pronto, Brian.

1215
01:22:56.824 --> 01:22:58.722
Sei molto silenzioso, Brian.

1216
01:23:01.476 --> 01:23:02.675
Va tutto bene?

1217
01:23:04.004 --> 01:23:04.753
Bene.

1218
01:23:09.205 --> 01:23:10.154
Che c'e'?

1219
01:23:14.974 --> 01:23:17.071
